  "text": "The SAO model equations used here are documented more completely in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] ; following is Values for constants are given in Table 1 . Besides active and leak Na + , K + , and Cl − currents, there is a bias current (I bias ), generated in response to muscle stretch, an active pump (I p ), and a synaptic current (I syn ). There are five gating variables, m, h, l, n, and r , with first-order kinetics described by equations A.7 to A.10 (where g ∈ {m, h, l, n, r }). dg/dt = (g ∞ − g) 1 τ g (A.7)",
